commit.message:
Merge branch 'master' of git://github.com/gdb/bunny

Conflicts:
	lib/bunny/session.rb
Use encode_to_array to avoid extra copies
Handle nil timeout, since system_timer does not
Use http://rubybunny.info as primary information source

Merge pull request #90 from gdb/master

Wait until basic_get_continuations has an element, not continuations
Wait until basic_get_continuations has an element, not continuations

Merge pull request #89 from gdb/master

Improve error handling capabilities for single-threaded applications

Where possible, don't rescue Exception

This allows single-threaded applications to set a Timeout and be
assured that no one will intercept it.
Raise a wrapped network error if not threaded
Move 'basic.get in a tight loop without network connection' workaround to Bunny::Channel#basic_get
